A brilliant bowling effort from India and Bangladesh are bowled out for 111! The final wicket is scalped by Rajvardhan Hangargekar, who takes his first scalp. Banged in short of good length, outside off stump,  Tanzim tries to pull, but the pace undoes him as he gets a top edge that is safely pouched by Vicky Ostwal near short square leg. 3 wickets for Ravi Kumar up front, Vicky Ostwal bags 2!
